modName: College of Winterhold to Star Wars Jedi Temple
summary: A re-texture of the College of Winterhold to look similar to a Jedi Temple
descriptionHtml:
College of Winterhold to Star Wars Jedi Temple


UPDATE
I've added the optional file for a blue floor instead of a red one.


I re-textured the College of Winterhold to look similar to a Jedi Temple. It does have a flaw though :-( The entry gate doesn't display the Jedi symbol properly. Unfortunately, There is nothing I can do about this without changing the mesh of the gate. Or at least I haven't found a way yet. I hope you all like it!
;-)

-avenger86
